negotiator.bidding

Class BidDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • negotiator.bidding.BidDetails
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BidDetails>

    public class BidDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<BidDetails>, java.io.Serializable
    The BidDetails class is used to store a bid with it's corresponding utility and time it was offered. In this way constant re-computation of the utility values is avoided.
    Author:
    Tim Baarslag, Alex Dirkzwager, Mark Hendrikx
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
